The paper proposes a novel pooling method for graph neural networks, which is a popular topic in machine learning research. The use of convolutional layers and pooling methods suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
